item.description:
I spend a lot of time thinking about build tools and popular setups, and what changes are more likely to impact developers positively. In one of these ramblings, one question popped up: &ldquo;How often do we change our builds?&rdquo;
It&rsquo;s not easier to answer this question, data on the topic is scarce. So I challenged myself to come up with some data to satisfy my curiosity.
Next I show some of the data I collected from Scala projects using sbt, the most popular Scala build tool.
